    Scope and Contents
Subject file of the Psychohistory Review, which contains files on the history of the publication, the Graduate Assistant's manual, a subscriber's list, several correspondence files from noteworthy contributors from around the world, and other important information concerning the publication, which ran for more than 25 years from 1972-1999.  
  
